#: ../../source/the_need_for.rst:34
msgid ""
"InVEST often employs a production function approach to quantifying and "
"valuing ecosystem services. A production function specifies the output of"
" ecosystem services provided by the environment given its condition and "
"processes. Once a production function is specified, we can quantify the "
"impact of changes on land or in the water on changes on the level of "
"ecosystem service output."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/the_need_for.rst:36
msgid ""
"InVEST uses a simple framework delineating “supply, service, and value” "
"to link production functions to the benefits provided to people (Figure "
"1)."
