#: ../../source/the_need_for.rst:122
msgid ""
"The spatial extent of analyses is also flexible, allowing users to "
"address questions at the local, regional or global scale. InVEST results "
"can be shared with the stakeholders and decision makers who created the "
"scenarios to inform upcoming decisions. Using InVEST is an iterative "
"process, and stakeholders may choose to create new scenarios based on the"
" information revealed by the models until suitable solutions for "
"management action are identified."
msgstr ""

